      <title class="- topic/title ">
         <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">52.219-13</ph> Notice of Set-Aside of Orders.</title>
      <conbody outputclass="clause" class="- topic/body  concept/conbody ">
         <p id="d3284e8" class="- topic/p ">As prescribed in <ph outputclass="ClauseProvisionXREF" class="- topic/ph ">
               <xref href="19.507.dita#FAR_19_507"
                     base="i1100931"
                     outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                     class="- topic/xref ">19.507</xref>(f)(1)</ph>, insert the following clause:</p>
         <p outputclass="Ctr_SmCaps" class="- topic/p " id="d3284e15">Notice of Set-Aside of Orders <ph outputclass="SmCaps" class="- topic/ph ">(Mar 2020)</ph>
         </p>
         <ol class="- topic/ol ">
            <li class="- topic/li ">
               <p id="d3284e21" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(a)</ph>
						            The Contracting Officer may set aside orders for the small business concerns identified in <xref href="19.000.dita#FAR_19_000"
                        base="i1101771"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">19.000</xref>(a)(3).</p>
            </li>
            <li class="- topic/li ">
               <p id="d3284e29" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(b)</ph>
						            The Contracting Officer will give notice of the order or orders, if any, to be set aside for small business concerns identified in <xref href="19.000.dita#FAR_19_000"
                        base="i1101771"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">19.000</xref>(a)(3) and the applicable small business program. This notice, and its restrictions, will apply only to the specific orders that have been set aside for any of the small business concerns identified in <xref href="19.000.dita#FAR_19_000"
                        base="i1101771"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">19.000</xref>(a)(3).</p>
            </li>
         </ol>
         <p outputclass="Endofclause" class="- topic/p ">(End of clause)</p>
         <section outputclass="Alternate" class="- topic/section "><?FM MARKER [Alt] Start?>
            <p id="id203KD0530BL" class="- topic/p ">
               <i class="+ topic/ph hi-d/i ">Alternate I <ph outputclass="SmCaps" class="- topic/ph ">(Mar 2020)</ph>
               </i>. As prescribed in <xref href="19.507.dita#FAR_19_507"
                     base="i1100931"
                     outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                     class="- topic/xref ">19.507</xref>(d), substitute the following paragraph (a) for paragraph (a) of the basic clause:</p>
            <p id="id203KD05A0PM" outputclass="List1" class="- topic/p ">(a) The Contracting Officer will set aside orders for the small business concerns identified in <xref href="19.000.dita#FAR_19_000"
                     base="i1101771"
                     outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                     class="- topic/xref ">19.000</xref>(a)(3) when the conditions of FAR <xref href="19.502-2.dita#FAR_19_502_2"
                     base="i1100762"
                     outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                     class="- topic/xref ">19.502-2</xref> and the specific program eligibility requirements are met, as applicable.</p>
            <?FM MARKER [Alt] End?>
         </section>
